{"tid":1787470,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊：三地三檢不等如剝奪司法管轄地區設關口權力","createTime":"2019-12-18T02:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T04:55:32.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eb57552f0342cbdb91a4f397fa529d951d86a5d6","tid":1787470,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:52:41.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊在電台節目回應，中國公安在港珠澳大橋東人工島設立安全檢查站，做法是否有違「三地三檢」時說，「三地三檢」並無令內地放棄行使司法管轄權，相關協議中提到，尊重屬地的司法管轄權原則，「三地三檢」不可視為剝奪某一司法管轄地區設立關口的權力，加上只是暫時措施，局外人不宜多加評論。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊又說，雖然不是入境內地，但進入了內地的地方，就要接受當地法律的管轄，例如有人已經在香港關口出境，但在機場候機室犯法，香港警方亦有權執法，強調已出境但未入境，不等如「無王管」。"},{"pid":"abeb4e83c2e17daaf3005e02cc1baa7104f33a97","tid":1787470,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:53:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1239873&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1239873%26csid%3D261_341&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2Bui2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=627c2730\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1239873&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"b3d9789af995050ab53ed6bdc8bfd1e158dcbdd4","tid":1787470,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:53:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雪</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"7b2e1f00bef27b53e24ff99129305dd21093d932","tid":1787470,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:55:57.000Z","msg":"衰11點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ee715f8f6e9a94c2f9793cc12b3efbd61bac57","tid":1787470,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3d9789af995050ab53ed6bdc8bfd1e158dcbdd4","tid":1787470,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201